FBIS4-41546 "drsov123_b_94017" FBIS-SOV-94-123 Daily Report 24 Jun 1994 RUSSIAN NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues FSK, Security Service Merger Report `Hoax' FSK, Security Service Merger Report `Hoax' LD2406150894 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1348 GMT 24 Jun 94 LD2406150894 Moscow INTERFAX English BFN [Text] Colonel Sergey Vasilyev, representative of the press section of the Federal Counterintelligence Service (FSK), refuted media information on possible combining of the FSK with the presidential Main Guarding Department and Security Service into a new special service. "There will be no reorganization, it's nothing more than another hoax," he said in his conversation with our Interfax correspondent.
